3 nights in the desert is a 2014 american drama film directed by gabriel cowan , written by adam &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and starring wes bentley , vincent piazza , and amber tamblyn . the film premiered on january 4 , 2014 , at the palm springs international film festival followed by a screening on october 18 , 2014 , at the twin cities film festival . the film will be given a limited release in early 2015 .